{"type": "article", "id": 22881, "title": "动物饲料包装设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-26T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133748eDVPNnQdmrXlofu8.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组大容量的动物饲料包装设计，选用了格外清爽的颜色。它的特征就是简洁直观，在每一包上面都印有对应动物的头像以便清楚辨认，是剪影的方式，非常统一。字体和图案也都是统一的颜色，可以减缓大体积的笨重感，带来健康自然的感受。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133745fAbQyvXjZ3wO2VPE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071337465P6RNgdOTVorGUBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071337468xE4kNTp6qm1oPwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133747dP527lqiNhpSFaMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133747P9nQTFmbUzgNE8XK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}